          "range": "13200-13305",
          "rangeStart": 13200,
          "rangeEnd": 13305,
          "markText": "这样，就使我们原来预计的战争进程，大为缩短。原来预计，从一九四六年七月起，大约需要五年左右时间，便可能从根本上打倒国民党反动政府。现在看来，只需从现时起，再有一年左右的时间，就可能将国民党反动政府从根本上打倒了",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1710383538,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-14 10:32:18",
          "chapterUid": 19,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6ej2vV2tv1iy6mm6ke7Db0Au&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=13200&rangeEnd=13305",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/08c42c83643425f36656a327656327476316979366d6d366b653744623041753a4?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=13200&rangeEnd=13305"
