          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/08c42c83643425f36656a327656327476316979366d6d366b653744623041753a4?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1944&rangeEnd=2004"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6ej2vV2tv1iy6mm6ke7Db0Au_18_5829-5882",
          "range": "5829-5882",
          "rangeStart": 5829,
          "rangeEnd": 5882,
          "markText": "锦州的战略地位十分重要。它地处东北和华北之交的走廊地带，一侧是高山，一侧是渤海，东有大凌河流经，地势险要。",
